mods.abstract: Map of Cyprus, showing: coastline, with capes and bays labelled; principal towns and villages; the route of the Cyprus Government Railway; principal roads; forested areas; topography, with heights indicated in feet; district boundaries, indicated by dotted lines. The map includes a printing statement which reads ‘Army Section 6 D. O. S. of I. No. 8506. July 1936.’
